    PanelPRO-22

    PanelPRO22.Rd

    Runs PanelPRO with 22 genes (genes = c("ATM", "BARD1", "BRCA1", "BRCA2", "BRIP1", "CDH1", "CDK4", "CDKN2A", "CHEK2", "EPCAM", "MLH1", "MSH2", "MSH6", "MUTYH", "NBN", "PALB2", "PMS2", "PTEN", "RAD51C", "RAD51D", "STK11", "TP53")) and 17 cancers (cancers = c("Brain", "Breast", "Colorectal", "Contralateral", "Endometrial", "Gastric", "Kidney", "Leukemia", "Melanoma", "Ovarian", "Osteosarcoma", "Pancreas", "Prostate", "Small Intestine", "Soft Tissue Sarcoma", "Thyroid", "Urinary Bladder", "Hepatobiliary")), as in PanelPRO:::MODELPARAMS$PanPRO22.

    PanelPRO22(...)

    Arguments

    ...

    Additional arguments to be passed into PanelPRO.

    See also

    PanelPRO

    Other predefined: BRCAPRO5(), BRCAPRO6(), BRCAPRO(), MMRPRO(), PanelPRO11()

    Examples

    data(test_fam_2)
PanelPRO22(test_fam_2, parallel = FALSE, max.mut = 1)
